
- Threashold contraint: x > 0 => x >= K
	x<= My
	x>= Ky
	y in {0, 1}

- Disjonctive constraint:   ti + di <= tj if i before j
                            tj + dj <= ti if j before i
	ti + di <= tj + M(1 - yij)
	tj + dj <= ti + M(yij)

- linearize xx' with x, x' in {0, 1} (introduce y = xx')
	y <= x
	y <= x'
	x + x' - 1 <= y
	y in {0, 1}
